{"lastModified":1754995975366,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: U.S. Virgin Islands, British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nTHE PURSUIT is a 18.89m / 62ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2021 by Lagoon. Sleeping 10 guests in 5 cabins and with a crew of 3. Cruising at 10.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise of 5 cabins with queen size beds and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"THE PURSUIT","images":["/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7VkkrDkXL.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-Rki6Rgnx7.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-IFa_TVahQ.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-Nsfe6AUXj.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-6rzU4pFGU.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-lWvbCeIZJ.jpg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::yachts-7706-BBizN45pM.jpg/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Lagoon","model":"","maxCrew":3,"sleeps":10,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::f8cef034-b3ed-11ed-a556-325096b39f47","name":"Nanny Cay","coordinates":{"latitude":18.40036609,"longitude":-64.63256083},"country":"British Virgin Islands"},"builtYear":2021,"cruiseSpeed":10,"cabins":5,"bathrooms":5,"length":18.89,"beam":9.78,"draft":1.55,"hullType":"Catamaran","superStructure":[],"engines":"2 x 110HP Volvo","amenities":[{"label":"Audio system","quantity":1},{"label":"Ice Maker","quantity":1},{"label":"Salon TV","quantity":1},{"label":"Generator","quantity":1},{"label":"Hammocks","quantity":1},{"label":"Special Diets","quantity":1},{"label":"Bimini","quantity":1},{"label":"Air Conditioning","quantity":1},{"label":"Onboard WiFI","quantity":1},{"label":"Deck shower","quantity":1},{"label":"Inverter","quantity":1},{"label":"Water Maker","quantity":1},{"label":"BBQ","quantity":1},{"label":"Salon Stereo","quantity":1},{"label":"iPod/Device Hookups","quantity":1},{"label":"BBQ","quantity":1},{"label":"Water Maker","quantity":1},{"label":"Air Conditioning","quantity":1},{"label":"iPod/Device Hookups","quantity":1},{"label":"Deck shower","quantity":1},{"label":"Inverter","quantity":1},{"label":"Salon Stereo","quantity":1},{"label":"Onboard WiFI","quantity":1},{"label":"Bimini","quantity":1}],"toys":[{"label":"Trolling Gear Type","quantity":4},{"label":"Inflatable Docks","quantity":1},{"label":"tubes","quantity":1},{"label":"Floating Mats","quantity":1},{"label":"E-foil","quantity":1},{"label":"2 Person Kayak","quantity":1},{"label":"Paddle-boards Stand Up (SUP)","quantity":2},{"label":"Sea Scooters","quantity":2},{"label":"Wakeboard","quantity":1},{"label":"Waterski Adult","quantity":1},{"label":"Snorkeling Gear","quantity":1},{"label":"Noodles","quantity":1},{"label":"Underwater Camera","quantity":1},{"label":"Underwater Video","quantity":1},{"label":"Fishing Gear","quantity":1},{"label":"Trolling and Casting Gear Type","quantity":1},{"label":"SeaBobs","quantity":1},{"label":"Beach Games","quantity":1},{"label":"Deep Sea Fishing Gear","quantity":1},{"label":"Dinghy (10 pax)"}]},"crew":[{"name":"Tristan Rogotzki","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::dad3b0f0-9f84-11ee-8a54-2ff0e01cb9ae.png/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Born to be a sailor, Tristan could say he had his sea legs before he even knew he had legs. His passion for freedom and love for the ocean and nature has always been a quintessential part of his personality.\n\nGrowing up in South Africa, Tristan became an avid sailboat racer, placing at a national level. This active lifestyle lead him to further explore the travel opportunities that can be provided stepping on board a charter vessel. His sailing career has brought him from Cape Agulhas, the Mediterranean, across the Atlantic, and now to the Caribbean.\n\nTristan enjoys spending as much time on the water as he does in the water, snorkeling and diving, and even over the water, playing with the videos he captures with his drone. Crossfit and hiking are other ways he loves to stay physically active and he always is up for a mental challenge in a game of chess."},{"name":"Hakim Tejada","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::e774c330-3baf-11f0-930f-3fcf044aa062/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Chef Hakim is 28 years old and hails from San Juan, PR. He has been professionally cooking for 12 years and on yachts for the last 5 years. He loves telling stories with his food and is very inspired by his travels. He is constantly incorporating lessons learned from his travels into his dishes to bring guests a unique and unforgettable culinary experience. Chef Hakim looks forward to having you on board!"},{"name":"Emily Hoppe","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::8275378522::vessel::d5cc4dda-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::11c1ecd0-3bb0-11f0-a55f-d706b0a91a9d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Originally from Chicago, Emily has spent the last five years living in San Juan, Puerto Rico, they have developed a deep love for the Caribbean and the sea. With over 10 years of experience in all aspects of the service industry, including extensive bartending and event planning, Emily is passionate about creating memorable experiences for her guests through her inventive cocktails and service that make guests feel right at home. Their enthusiasm for the sun, water, and vibrant culture of the Caribbean fuels their excitement for sailing. Dedicated to providing top-notch service and entertainment, Emily is ready to ensure that every moment aboard The Pursuit is enjoyable and unforgettable."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":4200000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":4200000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":4800000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":4800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Season","effectiveDates":[],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":4200000,"inputAmountTaxed":"INCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":1,"unitPrice":4200000,"amount":4200000}],"total":4200000,"subTotal":4200000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"St. Vin. and Gren.","type":"Sovereign country","category":["North America","Caribbean","St. Vin. and Gren."],"coordinates":[-61.23926839273057,13.08539492811089],"bbox":[-61.353515625,12.694726562499994,-61.1240234375,13.358740234374991]},{"label":"U.S. Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","U.S. Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.79221690684143,18.050874527948764],"bbox":[-65.0236328125,17.701708984375003,-64.58046875,18.385205078124997]},{"label":"British Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","British Virgin Is."],"coordinates":[-64.45080373172777,18.568736231458896],"bbox":[-64.69511718749999,18.399121093749997,-64.273583984375,18.752685546875]},{"label":"Caribbean Sea","type":"Custom Area","category":["Caribbean Sea"],"coordinates":[-75.20942221363948,15.447039028480969],"bbox":[-88.34899451369023,8.493693752471486,-59.20886105003194,22.689132188400592]},{"label":"Anguilla","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbean","Anguilla"],"coordinates":[-63.06498926535688,18.22395950228264],"bbox":[-63.16000976562499,18.17138671875,-62.97958984374999,18.269726562499997]},{"label":"Antigua and Barb.","type":"Sovereign country","category":["North America","Caribbean","Antigua and Bar